net.enilink.komma.model

Class ModelUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.enilink.komma.model.ModelUtil

  • public class ModelUtil
extends Object
    Utility methods for working with models and RDF data.

    Methods in this class are used to implement loading and saving of model data or to generate labels for visual representation of model elements.
